Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:14.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dear Nanoka Kohinata\NI know receiving a letter like this might\Nsurprise you. I've been interested in\Nyou since the first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Machida Marriage Consulting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350.641,48.329)}Special Event
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Matchmaking Party\NPlanning Overview
